and servicemax inc since march  he served as a director of hara software inc he served as a director of marketo inc from october  to august   and served as its lead independent director he served as a member of board of advisors at marketo inc until august   he served as an independent director of infogroup inc from january   to july  he served as a director of postini inc he served as a director of syniverse brience llc since may  he served as presiding director at dolby laboratories inc he served as lead director of cadence design systems inc since may  he served as a director of filenet corporation since  he served as a director of epiphany inc since august  he served as a director of active software inc since august  he served as a director of mandiant corporation corio inc pivotal software and macromedia inc he is a certified public accountant in new york and california mr siboni holds a bs degree in business administration from the university of california berkeleyread full background corporate headquarters  seely avenuesan jose california united statesphone fax  board members memberships presentindependent directorcadence design systems incpresentindependent directordolby laboratories incpresentindependent directorclassmates media corporationpresentdirectorironplanet incpresentdirectorarcsight incpresentdirectorrivet software incpresentlead independent directorcoupa software incorporatedpresentdirectorservicemax incpresentdirectormapr technologies inc education bsba university of california berkeley other affiliations active software inccorio incepiphany incfilenet corporationinfogroup incsyniverse brience llcileverage corporationironplanet incpostini incarcsight incdolby laboratories incuniversity of california berkeleyclassmates media corporationmandiant corporationrivet software inccoupa software incorporatedmarketo incservicemax inchara software incmapr technologies inc annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options ther